<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/37f42bb3-86ca-4420-a71d-41a2d4ea7457> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> _:b0__41860.
_:b0__41860 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((11.24 69.09,26.06 69.09,26.06 55.03,11.24 55.03,11.24 69.09))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
